'''澳洲醫療船-半人馬號'''{{Efn|The AHS is alternatively reported as standing for '''Army Hospital Ship'''.<ref name="DOD29-6-03">Department of Defence, ''Navy findings of search for ex Army Hospital Ship (AHS) Centaur''</ref>Also correctly referred to as '''2/3rd AHS ''Centaur''''' or '''AHS ''47'''''.<ref name=Mill51>Milligan and Foley, ''Australian Hospital Ship Centaur'', p. 51</ref> Also incorrectly referred to as '''HMAS ''Centaur'''''<ref name="Frame186-7">Frame, ''No Pleasure Cruise'', pp. 186–7</ref> or '''HMAHS ''Centaur'''''.<ref name=Mill51/>}}（{{lang-en|'''AHS Centaur'''}}）是一艘在1943年5月14日於[[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]]近岸水域被日軍[[伊號第百七十七潛艦|伊-177]]號潛艇擊沉的[[医疗船|醫療船]]。當時船上載有332名醫護人員及平民海員和65個陸軍人員，其中268人身亡，包括63個陸軍人員。

